--- requirements --------------------------------------------------------------

../theme

UpdateFilter:               emilis-stark-utils/react/update-filter

--- jade-react ----------------------------------------------------------------

div(
    class=  CLASSNAME
    class=  show && "shown"
)

--- livescript ----------------------------------------------------------------

_react-class <<< Update-filter

--- stylus --------------------------------------------------------------------

{SELECTOR}

    display                 none

    &.shown

        display             block
        position            fixed
        left                0
        top                 0
        right               0
        bottom              0
        z-index             9001

        background-image    url( /static/img/app-loading.svg )
        background-position 50% 50%
        background-repeat   no-repeat
        background-size     auto 60%
        background-color    $black

